Description_lang: While you are within your Death and Decay, your physical damage taken is reduced by ${$434034s1*-1}% and your chance to gain Vampiric Strike is increased by $s2%.

description_blz.en_US: While you are within your Death and Decay, your physical damage taken is reduced by 5% and your chance to gain Vampiric Strike is increased by 5%.
description_blz.es_MX: Mientras estás en tu Muerte y descomposición, el daño físico que recibes se reduce un 5%, y tu probabilidad de obtener Golpe vampírico aumenta un 5%.
description_blz.pt_BR: Enquanto estiver sobre sua runa de Morte e Decomposição, reduz em 5% o dano físico que você recebe e aumenta em 5% sua chance de ganhar Golpe Vampírico.
description_blz.de_DE: Während Ihr Euch in Eurem Bereich von 'Tod und Verfall' bewegt, ist Euer erlittener körperlicher Schaden um 5% verringert und Eure Chance, 'Vampirstoß' zu erhalten, um 5% erhöht.
description_blz.en_GB: While you are within your Death and Decay, your physical damage taken is reduced by 5% and your chance to gain Vampiric Strike is increased by 5%.
description_blz.es_ES: Mientras estás en el interior de tu Muerte y descomposición, el daño físico que recibes se reduce un 5% y tu probabilidad de obtener Golpe vampírico aumenta un 5%.
description_blz.fr_FR: Pendant que vous vous trouvez dans votre zone de Mort et décomposition, les dégâts physiques subis sont réduits de 5 % et les chances d’obtenir Frappe vampirique sont augmentées de 5 %.
description_blz.it_IT: Trovarsi all'interno di una propria Morte e Distruzione riduce i danni fisici subiti del 5% e aumenta la probabilità di ottenere Assalto Vampirico del 5%.
description_blz.ru_RU: Пока вы находитесь в области действия "Смерти и разложения", получаемый вами физический урон уменьшается на 5%, а вероятность получения "Удара вампира" увеличивается на 5%.
description_blz.ko_KR: 자신의 죽음과 부패 안에 있는 동안 받는 물리 피해가 5%만큼 감소하고 흡혈의 일격이 부여될 확률이 5%만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 當你在死亡凋零範圍內時，受到的物理傷害降低5%，且獲得吸血打擊的機率提高5%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 当你在你的枯萎凋零中时，你受到的物理伤害降低5%，获得吸血鬼打击的几率提高5%。
